metadata.description: A collection of 2,000 unique and playful pixelated ghosts that are sure to add a touch of spookiness to your digital collection. Each ghostly sprite is bursting with personality and charm, featuring a range of cute and creepy designs that will delight fans of all ages. Whether you're a seasoned NFT collector or a newcomer to the world of crypto art, "Spooky Sprites" is the perfect addition to your portfolio. Don't miss your chance to own a piece of this exclusive collection - each NFT is one-of-a-kind and once they're gone, they're gone forever!
metadata.name: Spooky Sprites #1
